                        <h1>API Docs</h1>
                        
						<p>The API is refreshed hourly. Polling much faster is a waste of time and bandwidth.</p>
						<p>The REST API can be accessed at <code>https://ixm.echoesofthe.net/api</code>. Currently, only GET requests are supported.</p>
						<p>Responses are returned in JSON.</p>
						<a href="#menu-toggle" class="btn btn-default" id="menu-toggle">Toggle Menu</a>
						<hr>
						<table class="table table-striped">
  							<tr>
